<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="雜科聲德" xml:id="gsz0897a10shiGuanXiu"><lb
ed="T" n="0897a10"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0897a10"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date>成都府東禪院<persName key="A005200">貫休</persName>傳（<persName key="A013946">處默</persName> <persName key="A013966">曇域</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0897a11"/><persName key="A005200">釋貫休</persName>，字<persName key="A005200">德隱</persName>，俗姓姜氏，<placeName key="PL000000013570">金華蘭溪登高</placeName>人<lb
ed="T" n="0897a12"/>也。<date key="j20271342027498" from-iso="+0838-01-01" to-iso="+0838-12-31">七歲</date>，父母雅愛之，投本縣<placeName key="PL000000013572">和安寺</placeName><persName key="A013959">圓貞禪<lb
ed="T" n="0897a13"/>師</persName>出家為童侍。日誦法華經一千字耳。所<lb
ed="T" n="0897a14"/>暫聞不忘於心。與<persName key="A013946">處默</persName>同削染，隣院而居，<lb
ed="T" n="0897a15"/>每隔籬論詩，互吟尋偶對，僧有見之，皆驚<lb
ed="T" n="0897a16"/>異焉。受具之後，詩名聳動於時，乃往<placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0897a17"/>傳法華經、起信論，皆精奧義，講訓且勤。本<lb
ed="T" n="0897a18"/>郡太守<persName key="A013960">王慥</persName>彌相篤重。次太守<persName key="A013961">蔣瓌</persName>開洗懺<lb
ed="T" n="0897a19"/>戒壇，命<persName key="A005200">休</persName>為監壇焉。<date key="j20476322048051" notAfter-iso="+0895-04-09" notBefore-iso="+0894-02-14"><name>乾寧</name>初</date>，齎志謁<placeName key="PL000000008355">吳越</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0897a20"/><persName key="A003552">武肅王錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>，因獻詩五章，章八句，甚愜旨，<lb
ed="T" n="0897a21"/>遺贈亦豐。王立去偽功，朝廷旌為功臣。乃<lb
ed="T" n="0897a22"/>別樹堂立碑，記同力平越將校姓名，遂刊<lb
ed="T" n="0897a23"/><persName key="A005200">休</persName>詩于碑陰，見重如此。<persName key="A005200">休</persName>善小筆，得六法。<lb
ed="T" n="0897a24"/>長於水墨，形似之狀可觀。受眾安橋強氏<lb
ed="T" n="0897a25"/>藥肆請，出羅漢一堂，云：「每畫一尊，必祈夢<lb
ed="T" n="0897a26"/>得應真貌，方成之。」與常體不同。自此遊<lb
ed="T" n="0897a27"/><placeName key="PL000000015693"><anchor xml:id="beg0897001"/>黟<anchor xml:id="end0897001"/></placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000015654">歙</placeName>，與唐安寺<!--找不到此地--><persName key="A013962">蘭闍梨</persName>道合。後思登<placeName key="PL000000028928">南<lb
ed="T" n="0897a28"/>嶽</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0897sgsz5"/>北<anchor xml:id="end0897sgsz5"/>謁<placeName key="PL000000027769">荊</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0897sgsz7"/>帥<anchor xml:id="end0897sgsz7"/><persName key="A012935">成汭</persName>，初甚禮焉，於龍興寺<!--找不到此地-->安<lb
ed="T" n="0897a29"/>置。時內翰<persName key="A013963">吳融</persName>謫官相遇，往來論道論詩。<pb ed="T" n="0897b" xml:id="T50.2061.0897b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0897b01"/><persName key="A013963">融</persName>為<persName key="A005200">休</persName>作集序，則<date key="j20483402048723" notAfter-iso="+0897-02-09" notBefore-iso="+0896-01-23"><name>乾寧</name>三年</date>也。尋被誣譖<lb
ed="T" n="0897b02"/>於荊<anchor xml:id="beg0897sgsz9"/>帥<anchor xml:id="end0897sgsz9"/>，黜<persName key="A005200">休</persName>于<placeName key="PL000000027790">功安</placeName>。欝悒中題硯子曰：「入<lb
ed="T" n="0897b03"/>匣始身安。」弟子勸<persName key="A005200">師</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>，時<ref type="person" target="#A006588">王氏</ref>將圖僣<lb
ed="T" n="0897b04"/>偽，邀四方賢士，得<persName key="A005200">休</persName>甚喜，盛被禮遇，賜賚<lb
ed="T" n="0897b05"/>隆洽，署號<persName key="A005200">禪月大師</persName>。<ref type="person" target="#A006588">蜀主</ref>常呼為「<persName key="A005200">得得來和<lb
ed="T" n="0897b06"/>尚</persName>」。時<persName key="A013964">韋藹</persName>舉其美號。所長者歌吟，諷刺微隱，<lb
ed="T" n="0897b07"/>存于教化。體調不下二李、<persName key="A005220">白</persName>、<persName key="A013965">賀</persName>也。至<date key="j20541872054363" notAfter-iso="+0912-07-21" notBefore-iso="+0912-01-27">梁乾<lb
ed="T" n="0897b08"/>化二年</date>終于所居，春秋八十一。<ref type="person" target="#A006588">蜀主</ref>慘怛，一<lb
ed="T" n="0897b09"/>皆官葬，塔號白蓮。於城都北門外昇遷為<lb
ed="T" n="0897b10"/>浮圖，乃偽蜀<date key="j20567572058940" notAfter-iso="+0925-01-31" notBefore-iso="+0919-02-09">乾德中</date>，即<date key="j20545912054924" notAfter-iso="+0914-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0913-03-06">梁<name>乾化</name>三年癸酉歲</date><lb
ed="T" n="0897b11"/>也。<persName key="A005200">休</persName>能草聖。出弟子<persName key="A013966">曇域</persName>，<date key="j20545912054924" notAfter-iso="+0914-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0913-03-06">癸酉年</date>集師文<lb
ed="T" n="0897b12"/>集，首安<persName key="A013963">吳內翰</persName>序，<persName key="A013966">域</persName>為後序。<persName key="A013967">韋莊</persName>甞贈詩<lb
ed="T" n="0897b13"/>曰：「豈是為窮常見隔，只應嫌酒不相過。」又<lb
ed="T" n="0897b14"/><persName key="A002039">廣成先生杜光庭</persName>相善，比鄉人也。<persName key="A005200">休</persName>書跡，好<lb
ed="T" n="0897b15"/>事者傳號曰姜體是也。甞覩<persName key="A005200">休</persName>真相，肥而<lb
ed="T" n="0897b16"/>矬，蜀宰相<persName key="A013968">王鍇</persName>作讚。<persName key="A013966">曇域</persName>戒學精微，篆文雄<lb
ed="T" n="0897b17"/>健，重集<persName key="A009285">許慎</persName>《說文》，見行于<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>。有詩集，亞師<lb
ed="T" n="0897b18"/>之體也。</p>
